OL,5, There is indignation in France after   
OL,6, the headteacher of a Paris school      
OL,7, resigned because of fears for his life.
OL,9,FThe head was sent death threats after  
OL,10,Fhe insisted that a teenage girl remove 
OL,11,Fher Islamic head-covering inside the   
OL,12,Fschool, in accordance with French law. 
OL,14,FHis name has not been made public. Two 
OL,15,Fpeople, who had no link with the       
OL,16,Fschool, have been detained.            
OL,18,FThe Islamist threat to French schools  
OL,19,Fis taken extremely seriously since the 
OL,20,Fmurders of two teachers.               
